{"tid":1910780,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"世界知識產權組織總幹事　由美國支持新加坡候選人當選","createTime":"2020-03-05T02:11:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T06:42:18.000Z","uid":48083,"like":261,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"d68953a6fbb4bef2bd89967549634294349025aa","tid":1910780,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T02:11:08.000Z","msg":"聯合國轄下的世界知識產權組織總幹事的選舉，由新加坡提名，並獲得美國支持的新加坡知識產權局局長鄧鴻森當選。<br />\n<br />\n鄧鴻森以55票對28票，擊敗現任副總幹事、中國提名的王彬穎。<br />\n<br />\n較早前，中國常駐聯合國日內瓦代表陳旭批評美國，在今次的總幹事選舉中，打壓王彬穎，批評美國將選舉當成政治博奕，用盡一切方法阻止王彬穎當選。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1512532-20200305.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1512532-20200305.htm&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbILtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=1f2df746\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1512532-20200305.htm&h=ea3e26db\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1512532-20200305.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0bd4a974b1d07860e42a812a145450863e05d4b9","tid":1910780,"uid":168698,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T02:13:30.000Z","msg":"中國賊喊抓賊，明明自己玩滲透結果睇其他國家都以為同自己一樣"},{"pid":"f9ad4bfaece4573e92474d4d977f05f7a49e0816","tid":1910780,"uid":7609,"like":105,"dislike":0,"score":105,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T02:15:03.000Z","msg":"贏唔到就話人阻止<br />\n支那狗識閪知識產權咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e7b37d5ae003db77819939cda58fb3bddf05b0e","tid":1910780,"uid":48531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T02:15:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e5b2078d628d9191e608405a44d2b21b43229fa","tid":1910780,"uid":168698,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T02:16:07.000Z","msg":"又黎西方威脅論"},{"pid":"4e11c823f823092257ec96e629618026f40fbdaf","tid":1910780,"uid":159913